subject: Little League
Little League World Series
Baseball
lead_paragraph: Mill Creek, Wash., got home runs from four players — including two from the left-handed slugger Alec Kisena — in a 16-hit attack that overpowered Hagerstown, Md., 15-5, in an elimination game at the Little League World Series in South Williamsport, Pa.
